1
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:15,800
What do you think we should do for the alliance banquet?

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:17,160
Su Cheng,

3
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:18,440
Mo Yu.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,080
Which one of you is Gu Chengyu?

5
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,400
What's wrong? You look worried.

6
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,200
Oh.

7
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:29,760
Didn't you ask me how to host the banquet well?

8
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:32,000
I was thinking,

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:34,480
instead of racking our brains on other things,

10
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:36,960
we should focus on the essence of the banquet:

11
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:37,890
delicious food.

12
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,160
That makes sense.

13
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,240
I thought of a dish

14
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,080
that will definitely amaze everyone.

15
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:44,240
What dish?

16
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:46,420
Flowers Competing in Beauty.

17
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:59,040
I want to use all the flowers in the world as ingredients

18
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:01,680
to make this Flowers Competing in Beauty.

19
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,800
It's a pity.

20
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,920
The world is so big.

21
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:09,280
When will we be able to find so many flowers?

22
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,120
Don't worry.

23
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:15,840
One day, I will help you realize this dream.

24
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:24,000
I didn't expect you to still remember.

25
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:26,640
I keep everything about you in my heart.

26
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,180
I will never forget it.

27
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,320
Yu.

28
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,960
You say it's just a small banquet.

29
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:51,759
But Su Cheng is full of tricks.

30
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,920
Plus Mu Jiuyun targets us everywhere.

31
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,759
How can I win?

32
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:00,880
Husband, look.

33
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:06,760
It turns out they've been having an affair.

34
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:11,840
It seems this time we can not only win the position of Minister of Revenue...

35
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:15,320
We can also eliminate these two big threats at once.

36
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:18,880
It's just a pity

37
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:22,360
that the yellow flower tree from our hometown isn't here.

38
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,120
If we had those yellow flowers,

39
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:26,600
this dream would be complete.

40
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,960
What's wrong?

41
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:33,800
Oh.

42
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,920
It's nothing.

43
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:39,720
I just remembered a place that has those yellow flowers.

44
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,280
I said, this is a forbidden area.

45
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,420
What are you doing here again?

46
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,820
I came to get some daylilies from you.

47
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,560
The princess will come to get some daylilies from you.

48
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,160
Remember to give them to her.

49
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,880
What are you going to do to the princess?

50
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,080
Tell me your plan.

51
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,640
When the time comes,

52
00:03:11,640 --> 00:03:13,100
I will naturally tell you.

53
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,840
Take it.

54
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,160
Is it you,

55
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,240
Gu Chengyu?

56
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,760
I am Mu Jiuyun.

57
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:58,400
A-Yun.

58
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:01,280
You are finally back.

59
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,200
I finally found you.

60
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:42,720
As for the position of Minister of Revenue,

61
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:44,720
I wonder who the Emperor has in mind.

62
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,840
In the first two competitions,

63
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:50,159
my two ministers performed exceptionally well.

64
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,760
They each won one round,

65
00:05:51,760 --> 00:05:53,280
resulting in a tie.

66
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,880
I really cannot say for sure.

67
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:58,970
But today's competition will definitely be exceptionally exciting.

68
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:03,080
The Vice Minister of Revenue has arrived.

69
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,080
Greetings, Your Majesties.

70
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:12,520
I prepared this for the alliance banquet.

71
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,160
The fine wine has arrived.

72
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:17,440
Please taste it, Your Majesties and my lords.

73
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:20,360
This wine is made by a winery in Beidi,

74
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,920
combined with the unique brewing techniques of our Great Jin.

75
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,600
Not only does it have a very special taste,

76
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:28,040
but it also symbolizes the friendship between our two countries and a shared prosperous age.

77
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:30,840
Great. Come, my lords.

78
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:33,540
Let us create a prosperous age together.

79
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,280
It indeed is good wine.

80
